title: LOVE Coming Home, LOVE Living Here! 3 Bedroom Apt. Available NOW!
posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', 'At The Legends of Columbia Heights, our independent 55+ apartment living community captures the essence of living well.', 'Enjoy the comforts of maintenance-free living along with the convenience of an outstanding location!', 'These one, two and three bedroom homes offer quality features such as granite kitchen countertops, spacious 9-foot ceilings, and a washer and dryer in every unit.', 'The Legends also provides a wealth of community amenities for you and your new neighbors – enjoy the beauty salon, 24-hour fitness center, craft room, theatre room, and community room with full kitchen and fireplace!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Community Library & Business Center', '- Full-Size Washer & Dryer', 'In EVERY Home!', '- State-Of-The-Art Fitness Center', '- Cards & Crafts Room', '- Guest-Suite', '- Gorgeous Community Room with Full Kitchen', '- Pet-Friendly Community', '- Additional Storage Available', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'The Legends of Columbia Heights is a 55 or better senior community and participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-4:30PM', 'Call today to schedule your tour:', 'show contact info', 'Legends of Columbia Heights', '3700 Huset Parkway', 'Columbia Heights, MN, 55421', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'INOn2OW4Jgt']
